@startuml
title Sequence Diagram: Image Editing
actor User
participant "UI (ImageEditorActivity)" as UI
participant "Image Processing Engine (OpenCV/Bitmap)" as Engine
participant "Local Storage" as Storage

== Open Image ==
User -> UI : Select Image
UI -> Storage : Read image stream
Storage --> UI : Bitmap data
UI --> User : Render Image Preview

== Edit Image (Filter/Rotate/Crop) ==
User -> UI : Apply Filter / Rotate / Crop
UI -> Engine : processImage(Bitmap, action, parameters)
activate Engine
Engine --> UI : Resulting Bitmap
deactivate Engine
UI --> User : Update Image Preview

== Save Edited Image ==
User -> UI : Click Save
UI -> Engine : compress and encode Bitmap
Engine --> UI : Byte Array
UI -> Storage : write to file
Storage --> UI : File URI / Success
UI --> User : Show "Image Saved"
@enduml
